{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290090/extras/600x100_1.jpg?t=1740157275\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Absolution is a first-person visual novel. In the eerie depths of this psychological thriller, face THE JUDGE and a twisted tale of grief, guilt and murder.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Confront your sins. Reflect on your morals. Liars will be punished.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290090/extras/Gameplay_Features.jpg?t=1740157275\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive Horror Experience</strong>: Come immerse yourself in an experience that blends eerie visuals with haunting soundscapes as an unnerving story unveils before you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unnerving Questions</strong>: Answer THE JUDGE\u2019s probing questions, where honesty is key\u2014liars will be punished.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chilling Narrative</strong>: Witness the unraveling of a tale filled with desperation, guilt, and the lingering hope for redemption.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Compelling Characters</strong>: Meet the characters of this horrific story. Can they be saved from their fatal fates?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3290090/extras/About_Development.jpg?t=1740157275\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Absolution was developed within the University of Southern California's Games Program. For more information about the USC Games Program, check out their website.</p></li></ul>","background":"https